question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Hur många människor bodde i Odense kommun, Danmark den 1 juli 2022?
answer: Den 1 juli 2022 hade Odense kommun i Danmark cirka 206,305 invånare.
answer_translated_eng: On 1 July 2022, Odense Municipality in Denmark had around 206,305 inhabitants.
